03:55.960 --> 03:57.920
Well, um...

03:59.160 --> 04:01.280
And so, when did this...

04:02.160 --> 04:03.000
when did this happen?

04:03.080 --> 04:04.440
-11 years ago.

04:14.400 --> 04:15.400
OK.

04:16.080 --> 04:16.960
Um...

04:19.960 --> 04:22.120
So, here's the thing. Um...

04:22.800 --> 04:25.440
