when you reported him missing?

05:27.640 --> 05:29.840
Well, I didn't want him
to get into trouble.

05:30.480 --> 05:33.760
He's a weird kid, but he's not bad.

05:34.120 --> 05:36.320
Uh, who did that to you?

05:36.400 --> 05:38.320
I just got into a fight.

05:38.560 --> 05:39.680
