06:50.520 --> 06:53.120
<i>It's better if I go to my dad's</i>
<i>on my own, anyway.</i>

06:54.840 --> 06:57.360
<i>I wish I hadn't left James</i>
<i>with the money, though.</i>

07:00.800 --> 07:02.000
<i>Oh, God.</i>

07:03.120 --> 07:04.640
<i>I'd really like it if this was</i>

07:04.720 --> 07:07.600
