08:15.840 --> 08:19.760
We're going to need
a recent photograph of Alyssa. Um...

08:22.960 --> 08:24.080
Do you have one?

08:26.200 --> 08:28.040
I've got some upstairs.

08:35.559 --> 08:39.480
I can recommend
Childline or the NSPCC.

08:45.840 --> 08:47.040
OK, will do.

08:47.480 --> 08:48.480
Thanks.

08:52.960 --> 08:58.120
So, I've been speaking to my DI,
that was him on the phone there.

08:59.160 --> 09:01.320
What we thought would be
the best thing is if we put you

09:01.400 --> 09:03.240
